About this item

  • Accurate Pedometer Watch--- This stand-alone fitness watch requires no connection to an app or cell phone. Perfect for those looking for a straightforward fitness tracker that operates independently without a smartphone. Automatically accurate to track your all-day or a period of time steps, makes fitness fun
  • No Need for Charging Fitness Tracker--- This sport watch does not have regular chargind, endurance, use more convenient
  • Multifuctional Outdoors Watch--- Stopwatch, Countdown Timer, Alarm Clock, Calendar with Week/Year/Month/Day, LED backlight, Dual Time Display, Step Counter, Calories Counter, Distance, 12/24 Military Time. These features make it the perfect choice for all kinds of outdoor sports and everyday use, such as running, walking, swimming, hiking...
  • IP68 Waterproof--- Water resistant to 165 feet (5ATM/50M) , suitable for swimming and showering , but please DO NOT PRESS any BUTTONS in the water , Avoid using it in extreme hot or cold temperature
  • Fashion Military Tactical Watch--- Best Gift for the men you love, suitable as a special festival gift, birthday gift, Valentine's Day, anniversary, business, birthday, Thanksgiving Day, Christmas etc
